<li><a href="/wiki/Indus_Valley_Civilization" title="Indus Valley Civilization">Indus Valley Civilization</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mauryan" title="Mauryan" class="mw-redirect">Mauryan</a> and <a href="/wiki/Gupta_Empire" title="Gupta Empire">Gupta</a> states</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Angkor_Wat" title="Angkor Wat">Angkor civilization</a> of the <a href="/wiki/Khmer_Empire" title="Khmer Empire">Khmer Empire</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Han_Dynasty" title="Han Dynasty">Han</a> and <a href="/wiki/Tang_Dynasty" title="Tang Dynasty">Tang Dynasty</a> of <a href="/wiki/Chinese_History" title="Chinese History" class="mw-redirect">China</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Anasazi" title="Anasazi" class="mw-redirect">Anasazi</a></li>
